intro: Demo of locking the direction the player can move in.
name: Twisty Little Maze

__comments: what's up with the target tile?
allow passage through gateways that are aligned with direction of movement
generally limit movement to either horizontal or vertical
when "A" is pressed, toggle between horizontal movement and vertical movement
don't allow sneaking through doors that are closing
NOTE: gate is "closed" when direction and gate are not aligned, so any gate
NOTE: that goes vertical when direction is "horizontal" will be closed
